reviewText: Great to watch the old cartoons. The new so called cartoons are a joke. Love to watch these.
this item was not AS DESCRIBED. there is ONE or TWO episodes of WOODYWOODPECKER AND I THINK ONE CASPER. GOOD ITEM FOR MONEY, GOOD SHIPPING TIME--but this item is not the one I ORDERED.

I purchased this for my nephew for his birthday. He loves the cartoons that me and his dad watched when we were young.
These cartoons are so much better than the ones on now unless you can go to an oldies but goodies station.
You can laugh out loud and not worry about waking up your folks !!  These are the "good ones" that were stuck in between all the other cartoons!!
It's an okay DVD but, beware some of the cartoons may be offensive, mainly to Natives and Black people.

Good,clean fun...from bygone days! POPEYE and BETTY BOOP are hilarious!
If you like cartoons and want to laugh......don't miss this collection.
The Big E
the only thing that was wrong was the case that the movie was in was cracked but the movies still worked thanks
